### Step 8: Schema Migration for Question Answer Fields

**File: `/Users/marcus/conductor/workspaces/brain/santo-domingo-v1/schema/migrations/0013_question_answer_fields.surql`** (new)

```sql
-- Add answer tracking fields to question table
BEGIN TRANSACTION;

DEFINE FIELD OVERWRITE answer_summary ON question TYPE option<string>;
DEFINE FIELD OVERWRITE answered_at ON question TYPE option<datetime>;
DEFINE FIELD OVERWRITE answered_by_message ON question TYPE option<record<message>>;

