```

The `status` field on `question` is already a free string (no ASSERT constraint on values), so "asked", "answered", "deferred" values work without schema changes. However, check if there is a constraint -- from the schema exploration, `status` on question is `TYPE string` with no ASSERT, so free values are fine.

